{"tid":1613494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈嚴禁任何形式分化 只檢討 不指責","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:48:46.000Z","uid":49813,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59d3ccf4559b75c6f529aacc9024d99e50a68645","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"我警告大家<br />\n事後檢討成敗得失完全無問題<br />\n咪撚再屌咩一區撚 民意撚 冷氣軍師 港豬和理非 前線勇武<br />\n你地屌人個陣有無諗過被屌既人會挫敗 會灰心 會失去戰意<br />\n無人會永遠正確 呢類負面情緒好快會漫延開去<br />\n記唔記得雨革衰咩啊!?<br />\n分化啊<br />\n<br />\n屌人之前 <br />\n諗下義士既傷口 中槍既一幕<br />\n你屌個刻就已經佢義士唔住<br />\n因為你分化緊佢地帶來既團結啊!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=542398913195804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D542398913195804&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=896d4ef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=542398913195804</a>"},{"pid":"ff3d04a20d25781e95a7fc686f969bd8d328d17e","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"自推1/100"},{"pid":"4bbd7a04846881c4c47e0cf5f345bbb2d7db2ce1","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"自推2/100"},{"pid":"f2fab3193a3aa535761b2902925a78eb21da1cb6","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"自推3/100"},{"pid":"0fa030140af5521aba49ce9642d4a26defaa4dd9","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"自推4/100"},{"pid":"ee20f8d8fb2c88ae34de981dcf27365b2052ed16","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"自推5/100"},{"pid":"fbdd0f7902276b6115c5f8f81b5aa11585a2a745","tid":1613494,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"自推6/100"},{"pid":"d